-- Hong Kong Stocks Fall Before China Manufacturing Data
-- B y   J o n a t h a n   B u r g o s
-- 2013-03-21T01:39:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-21/hong-kong-stocks-fall-before-china-manufacturing-data.html
Hong Kong  stocks  rose for a second
day, ahead of a release of a report on Chinese manufacturing.  The  Hang Seng Index (HSI)  added 0.1 percent to 22,262.60 as of
9:38 a.m. in Hong Kong.  To contact the reporter on this story:
